Section [0] Other types of albedo
Text: '
'
Begin Reference: Single scattering albedo
End Reference: Single scattering albedo
Text: ' is used to define scattering of electromagnetic waves on small particles. It depends on properties of the material ('
Begin Reference: refractive index
End Reference: refractive index
Text: '); the size of the particle or particles; and the wavelength of the incoming radiation.

